{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":606,"text":"I recently retired"},{"time":1744,"text":"from the California Highway Patrol"},{"time":3788,"text":"after 23 years of service."},{"time":6725,"text":"The majority of those 23 years"},{"time":8691,"text":"was spent patrolling the southern end"},{"time":11319,"text":"of Marin County,"},{"time":12852,"text":"which includes the Golden Gate Bridge."},{"time":16029,"text":"The bridge is an iconic structure,"},{"time":18316,"text":"known worldwide"},{"time":19569,"text":"for its beautiful views of San Francisco,"},{"time":22245,"text":"the Pacific Ocean, and its inspiring architecture."}]},{"cues":[{"time":26636,"text":"Unfortunately, it is also a magnet for suicide,"},{"time":31052,"text":"being one of the most utilized sites in the world."},{"time":35631,"text":"The Golden Gate Bridge opened in 1937."},{"time":38761,"text":"Joseph Strauss, chief engineer\nin charge of building the bridge,"},{"time":43084,"text":"was quoted as saying,"},{"time":44688,"text":"\"The bridge is practically suicide-proof."},{"time":48084,"text":"Suicide from the bridge"},{"time":49793,"text":"is neither practical nor probable.\""},{"time":53559,"text":"But since its opening,"},{"time":55853,"text":"over 1,600 people have leapt to their death"},{"time":59000,"text":"from that bridge."},{"time":61162,"text":"Some believe that traveling"},{"time":63366,"text":"between the two towers"},{"time":65431,"text":"will lead you to another dimension --"},{"time":67554,"text":"this bridge has been romanticized as such â€”"},{"time":71010,"text":"that the fall from that"},{"time":72589,"text":"frees you from all your worries and grief,"},{"time":75623,"text":"and the waters below"},{"time":77407,"text":"will cleanse your soul."}]},{"cues":[{"time":79531,"text":"But let me tell you what actually occurs"},{"time":81855,"text":"when the bridge is used"},{"time":83041,"text":"as a means of suicide."},{"time":85095,"text":"After a free fall of four to five seconds,"},{"time":88549,"text":"the body strikes the water"},{"time":91218,"text":"at about 75 miles an hour."},{"time":94900,"text":"That impact shatters bones,"},{"time":97617,"text":"some of which then puncture vital organs."},{"time":100969,"text":"Most die on impact."},{"time":103318,"text":"Those that don't"},{"time":105070,"text":"generally flail in the water helplessly,"},{"time":107663,"text":"and then drown."},{"time":109882,"text":"I don't think that those who contemplate"},{"time":112050,"text":"this method of suicide"},{"time":113872,"text":"realize how grisly a death that they will face."},{"time":119048,"text":"This is the cord."},{"time":121176,"text":"Except for around the two towers,"},{"time":123233,"text":"there is 32 inches of steel"},{"time":125521,"text":"paralleling the bridge."},{"time":127051,"text":"This is where most folks stand"},{"time":129336,"text":"before taking their lives."},{"time":131870,"text":"I can tell you from experience"},{"time":133904,"text":"that once the person is on that cord,"},{"time":136638,"text":"and at their darkest time,"},{"time":138396,"text":"it is very difficult to bring them back."},{"time":141690,"text":"I took this photo last year"},{"time":143732,"text":"as this young woman spoke to an officer"},{"time":145668,"text":"contemplating her life."},{"time":147666,"text":"I want to tell you very happily"},{"time":149922,"text":"that we were successful that day"},{"time":152030,"text":"in getting her back over the rail."}]},{"cues":[{"time":154954,"text":"When I first began working on the bridge,"},{"time":157346,"text":"we had no formal training."},{"time":159830,"text":"You struggled to funnel your\nway through these calls."},{"time":163624,"text":"This was not only a disservice"},{"time":166088,"text":"to those contemplating suicide,"},{"time":168127,"text":"but to the officers as well."},{"time":170920,"text":"We've come a long, long way since then."},{"time":174100,"text":"Now, veteran officers and psychologists"},{"time":177669,"text":"train new officers."}]},{"cues":[{"time":180340,"text":"This is Jason Garber."},{"time":182549,"text":"I met Jason on July 22 of last year"},{"time":185760,"text":"when I get received a call"},{"time":186875,"text":"of a possible suicidal subject"},{"time":188817,"text":"sitting on the cord near midspan."},{"time":191566,"text":"I responded, and when I arrived,"},{"time":194263,"text":"I observed Jason"},{"time":196077,"text":"speaking to a Golden Gate Bridge officer."},{"time":199448,"text":"Jason was just 32 years old"},{"time":201972,"text":"and had flown out here from New Jersey."},{"time":204804,"text":"As a matter of fact,"},{"time":206348,"text":"he had flown out here on two other occasions"},{"time":208166,"text":"from New Jersey"},{"time":209928,"text":"to attempt suicide on this bridge."},{"time":213342,"text":"After about an hour of speaking with Jason,"},{"time":216900,"text":"he asked us if we knew the story of Pandora's box."},{"time":220635,"text":"Recalling your Greek mythology,"},{"time":223070,"text":"Zeus created Pandora,"},{"time":225040,"text":"and sent her down to Earth with a box,"},{"time":228394,"text":"and told her, \"Never, ever open that box.\""},{"time":232298,"text":"Well one day, curiosity got the better of Pandora,"},{"time":234940,"text":"and she did open the box."},{"time":237342,"text":"Out flew plagues, sorrows,"},{"time":240194,"text":"and all sorts of evils against man."},{"time":243406,"text":"The only good thing in the box was hope."},{"time":247985,"text":"Jason then asked us,"},{"time":250558,"text":"\"What happens when you open the box"},{"time":253542,"text":"and hope isn't there?\""},{"time":256724,"text":"He paused a few moments,"},{"time":259774,"text":"leaned to his right,"},{"time":262213,"text":"and was gone."},{"time":264414,"text":"This kind, intelligent young man from New Jersey"},{"time":268284,"text":"had just committed suicide."}]},{"cues":[{"time":272064,"text":"I spoke with Jason's parents that evening,"},{"time":275064,"text":"and I suppose that, when I was speaking with them,"},{"time":277626,"text":"that I didn't sound as if I was doing very well,"},{"time":281390,"text":"because that very next day,"},{"time":283610,"text":"their family rabbi called to check on me."},{"time":287130,"text":"Jason's parents had asked him to do so."},{"time":290924,"text":"The collateral damage of suicide"},{"time":293132,"text":"affects so many people."}]},{"cues":[{"time":298235,"text":"I pose these questions to you:"},{"time":301216,"text":"What would you do if your family member,"},{"time":303884,"text":"friend or loved one was suicidal?"},{"time":306992,"text":"What would you say?"},{"time":309426,"text":"Would you know what to say?"},{"time":312656,"text":"In my experience, it's not just the talking that you do,"},{"time":316582,"text":"but the listening."},{"time":318830,"text":"Listen to understand."},{"time":323446,"text":"Don't argue, blame,"},{"time":325974,"text":"or tell the person you know how they feel,"},{"time":329742,"text":"because you probably don't."},{"time":332353,"text":"By just being there,"},{"time":335264,"text":"you may just be the turning point that they need."},{"time":339587,"text":"If you think someone is suicidal,"},{"time":342691,"text":"don't be afraid to confront\nthem and ask the question."},{"time":346405,"text":"One way of asking them the question is like this:"},{"time":350615,"text":"\"Others in similar circumstances"},{"time":353029,"text":"have thought about ending their life;"},{"time":355197,"text":"have you had these thoughts?\""},{"time":357956,"text":"Confronting the person head-on"},{"time":360752,"text":"may just save their life and\nbe the turning point for them."},{"time":364702,"text":"Some other signs to look for:"},{"time":367151,"text":"hopelessness, believing that things are terrible"},{"time":371299,"text":"and never going to get better;"},{"time":374426,"text":"helplessness, believing that there is nothing"},{"time":377871,"text":"that you can do about it;"},{"time":380303,"text":"recent social withdrawal;"},{"time":382900,"text":"and a loss of interest in life."}]},{"cues":[{"time":387717,"text":"I came up with this talk just a couple of days ago,"},{"time":391639,"text":"and I received an email from a lady"},{"time":394840,"text":"that I'd like to read you her letter."},{"time":399325,"text":"She lost her son on January 19 of this year,"},{"time":407437,"text":"and she wrote this me this email"},{"time":409250,"text":"just a couple of days ago,"},{"time":412620,"text":"and it's with her permission and blessing"},{"time":414620,"text":"that I read this to you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":417645,"text":"\"Hi, Kevin. I imagine you're at the TED Conference."},{"time":421647,"text":"That must be quite the experience to be there."},{"time":424581,"text":"I'm thinking I should go walk\nthe bridge this weekend."},{"time":428213,"text":"Just wanted to drop you a note."},{"time":430746,"text":"Hope you get the word out to many people"},{"time":432967,"text":"and they go home talking about it"},{"time":435079,"text":"to their friends who tell their friends, etc."},{"time":439745,"text":"I'm still pretty numb,"},{"time":442189,"text":"but noticing more moments of really realizing"},{"time":445261,"text":"Mike isn't coming home."},{"time":447973,"text":"Mike was driving from Petaluma to San Francisco"},{"time":450720,"text":"to watch the 49ers game with his father"},{"time":452637,"text":"on January 19."},{"time":454670,"text":"He never made it there."},{"time":457614,"text":"I called Petaluma police"},{"time":459661,"text":"and reported him missing that evening."},{"time":462157,"text":"The next morning,"},{"time":464059,"text":"two officers came to my home"},{"time":467782,"text":"and reported that Mike's car was down at the bridge."},{"time":472286,"text":"A witness had observed him jumping off the bridge"},{"time":474750,"text":"at 1:58 p.m. the previous day."},{"time":479002,"text":"Thanks so much"},{"time":481622,"text":"for standing up for those"},{"time":482806,"text":"who may be only temporarily too weak"},{"time":485358,"text":"to stand for themselves."},{"time":487900,"text":"Who hasn't been low before"},{"time":489920,"text":"without suffering from a true mental illness?"},{"time":493696,"text":"It shouldn't be so easy to end it."},{"time":497057,"text":"My prayers are with you for your fight."},{"time":500454,"text":"The GGB, Golden Gate Bridge,"},{"time":504050,"text":"is supposed to be a passage across"},{"time":506776,"text":"our beautiful bay,"},{"time":508859,"text":"not a graveyard."},{"time":511546,"text":"Good luck this week. Vicky.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":516810,"text":"I can't imagine the courage it takes for her"},{"time":519853,"text":"to go down to that bridge and walk the path"},{"time":521795,"text":"that her son took that day,"},{"time":525233,"text":"and also the courage just to carry on."}]},{"cues":[{"time":530307,"text":"I'd like to introduce you to a man"},{"time":534053,"text":"I refer to as hope and courage."},{"time":539695,"text":"On March 11 of 2005,"},{"time":542334,"text":"I responded to a radio call of a possible"},{"time":544997,"text":"suicidal subject on the bridge sidewalk"},{"time":547211,"text":"near the north tower."},{"time":548699,"text":"I rode my motorcycle down the sidewalk"},{"time":551387,"text":"and observed this man, Kevin Berthia,"},{"time":554099,"text":"standing on the sidewalk."},{"time":556635,"text":"When he saw me, he immediately traversed"},{"time":560060,"text":"that pedestrian rail,"},{"time":562237,"text":"and stood on that small pipe"},{"time":563109,"text":"which goes around the tower."},{"time":566181,"text":"For the next hour and a half,"},{"time":568515,"text":"I listened as Kevin spoke about"},{"time":571443,"text":"his depression and hopelessness."},{"time":574331,"text":"Kevin decided on his own that day"},{"time":577005,"text":"to come back over that rail"},{"time":578687,"text":"and give life another chance."},{"time":581419,"text":"When Kevin came back over,"},{"time":583190,"text":"I congratulated him."},{"time":585231,"text":"\"This is a new beginning, a new life.\""},{"time":587981,"text":"But I asked him, \"What was it"},{"time":591015,"text":"that made you come back"},{"time":592740,"text":"and give hope and life another chance?\""},{"time":595530,"text":"And you know what he told me?"},{"time":598221,"text":"He said, \"You listened."},{"time":600751,"text":"You let me speak, and you just listened.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":605951,"text":"Shortly after this incident,"},{"time":607910,"text":"I received a letter from Kevin's mother,"},{"time":611169,"text":"and I have that letter with me,"},{"time":614081,"text":"and I'd like to read it to you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":616931,"text":"\"Dear Mr. Briggs,"},{"time":619087,"text":"Nothing will erase the events of March 11,"},{"time":621952,"text":"but you are one of the reasons Kevin is still with us."},{"time":625080,"text":"I truly believe Kevin was crying out for help."},{"time":629373,"text":"He has been diagnosed with a mental illness"},{"time":632095,"text":"for which he has been properly medicated."},{"time":634929,"text":"I adopted Kevin when he was only six months old,"},{"time":638297,"text":"completely unaware of any hereditary traits,"},{"time":642245,"text":"but, thank God, now we know."},{"time":646429,"text":"Kevin is straight, as he says."},{"time":649255,"text":"We truly thank God for you."},{"time":651940,"text":"Sincerely indebted to you,"},{"time":654341,"text":"Narvella Berthia.\""},{"time":657033,"text":"And on the bottom she writes,"},{"time":659081,"text":"\"P.S. When I visited San Francisco\nGeneral Hospital that evening,"},{"time":664517,"text":"you were listed as the patient."},{"time":666445,"text":"Boy, did I have to straighten that one out.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":671427,"text":"Today, Kevin is a loving father"},{"time":675557,"text":"and contributing member of society."},{"time":678242,"text":"He speaks openly"},{"time":679711,"text":"about the events that day and his depression"},{"time":682645,"text":"in the hopes that his story"},{"time":684327,"text":"will inspire others."}]},{"cues":[{"time":687401,"text":"Suicide is not just something\nI've encountered on the job."},{"time":690831,"text":"It's personal."},{"time":692863,"text":"My grandfather committed suicide by poisoning."},{"time":696737,"text":"That act, although ending his own pain,"},{"time":700611,"text":"robbed me from ever getting to know him."},{"time":705157,"text":"This is what suicide does."},{"time":707823,"text":"For most suicidal folks,"},{"time":710171,"text":"or those contemplating suicide,"},{"time":712125,"text":"they wouldn't think of hurting another person."},{"time":714831,"text":"They just want their own pain to end."},{"time":718415,"text":"Typically, this is accomplished in just three ways:"},{"time":722451,"text":"sleep, drugs or alcohol, or death."},{"time":728109,"text":"In my career, I've responded to"},{"time":730829,"text":"and been involved in hundreds"},{"time":733182,"text":"of mental illness and suicide calls"},{"time":735960,"text":"around the bridge."},{"time":737754,"text":"Of those incidents I've been directly involved with,"},{"time":741265,"text":"I've only lost two,"},{"time":743237,"text":"but that's two too many."},{"time":745423,"text":"One was Jason."},{"time":747435,"text":"The other was a man I spoke to"},{"time":749691,"text":"for about an hour."},{"time":751374,"text":"During that time, he shook my hand"},{"time":753790,"text":"on three occasions."},{"time":756527,"text":"On that final handshake,"},{"time":758603,"text":"he looked at me, and he said,"},{"time":760937,"text":"\"Kevin, I'm sorry, but I have to go.\""},{"time":766340,"text":"And he leapt."},{"time":768473,"text":"Horrible, absolutely horrible."}]},{"cues":[{"time":771279,"text":"I do want to tell you, though,"},{"time":773255,"text":"the vast majority of folks"},{"time":775607,"text":"that we do get to contact on that bridge"},{"time":779129,"text":"do not commit suicide."},{"time":782325,"text":"Additionally, that very few"},{"time":785315,"text":"who have jumped off the bridge and lived"},{"time":787971,"text":"and can talk about it,"},{"time":789317,"text":"that one to two percent,"},{"time":792130,"text":"most of those folks have said"},{"time":793961,"text":"that the second that they let go of that rail,"},{"time":797315,"text":"they knew that they had made a mistake"},{"time":799880,"text":"and they wanted to live."},{"time":802931,"text":"I tell people, the bridge not only connects"},{"time":807364,"text":"Marin to San Francisco,"},{"time":809645,"text":"but people together also."},{"time":812837,"text":"That connection, or bridge that we make,"},{"time":816630,"text":"is something that each and every one of us"},{"time":819059,"text":"should strive to do."},{"time":821053,"text":"Suicide is preventable."},{"time":824077,"text":"There is help. There is hope."}]},{"cues":[{"time":827411,"text":"Thank you very much."}]},{"cues":[{"time":830441,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}